==Dutch==

===verb===
'''schreeuwen'''
# To [[yell]]; to [[bellow]]; to [[shout]]; to [[talk]] [[loudly]].
# To [[scream]]; to [[shriek]].
# Of a colour or design: to be extremely [[conspicuous]].
#: ''Dit behang schreeuwt nogal.'' &mdash; This wallpaper is very loud.

